<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Wikiful</title>
  	<!--[if lt IE 9]>
  	<script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<![endif]-->
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head> 
<body>
<div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
	<div class="navbar-inner">
		<div class="container">
			<%= link_to "Wikiful", root_path, :class => "brand" %>
				<div class='session-controls'>
					<% if current_user %>
						<%= link_to "Log Out", logout_path, :class => 'btn btn-primary btn-mini' %>						Logged in as <%= current_user.email %>.
					<% else %>
						<div class="btn-group">
							<%= link_to "Sign Up", signup_path, :class => "btn btn-mini" %>
							<%= link_to "Log In", login_path, :class => "btn btn-mini" %>
						</div>
					<% end %> 
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

<div class="row">
	<div class="span4">
		<% flash.each do |name, msg| %>
			<%= content_tag :div, msg, id: "flash_#{name}" %>
		<% end %>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="span3 sidebar">
	<div class="my-wiki-site">
		<img src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qSBLtcVU-h0/UL_1BwC1l_I/AAAAAAAABjg/6NCOAQfX9MY/s1600/m123194294.gif" width="171" height="313">
		<li class="nav-header" font_size: >Wikiful</li>
		<ul>
			<li><%= link_to "Write a Wiki", new_article_path %></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
<div class="categories-sidebar">
	<li class="nav-header">Categories</li>
		<ul class="nav nav-list">
			<% @categories.each do |category| %>
				<li><%= link_to category.name, category %></li>
			<% end %>
		</ul>
	</div>
<div class="about">
	<h4>About Wikiful</h4>
		<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Accusantium architecto earum neque perspiciatis quia animi debitis quod repellat vitae explicabo. Sapiente aliquam reprehenderit id vitae atque ducimus facere molestias soluta?</p>
	</div>
</div>
<%= yield %> 

</body>
</html>
